caption:
As they transitioned out of the “puppy love” stage, Anne and Danny turned to a Talkspace couples therapist so they could learn to handle conflict in a healthy way and make their bond even stronger 💞.

Did you know that many insurance plans cover couples therapy? Talkspace is in-network with major insurance companies, which means that most Talkspace members pay only a copay ($15 on average, and most covered members pay $0).
